Ocosta Elementary Student Council is at Ocosta Elementary School.
January 23, 2015 at 11:00 AM · Westport, WA ·

Rainy, wet, Westport winter day; but they're busy drilling holes - there is a lot of activity today.

post_text: It sounds complicated - drilling a hole, injecting cement while pulling the drill out, and then installing the rebar to reinforce the piling (we were told that the rebar cage had to be "jiggled" in to the cement). There's not a lot of action in this video, but at about the 1 minute 20 second mark you can see them start putting in the rebar cage - it takes only seconds for it to settle into the fresh cement.
